name: OMNISCIENCE
description:
Created by @MathMakesArt (https://mathmakes.art) on 2021/10/08. 1600 px square generated in p5.js.

This is my first mint since the release of the MATH token.
The main primary sale period will continue until at least 2021/10/16 and at most 2021/11/07.
After this point, some number of editions will be saved, equal to no more than 15.0% of the sold supply (if 100 copies are sold, a maximum of 15 additional copies will be set aside).
The remaining editions not set aside will be BURNED at the end of the main primary sale period.
The extra copies saved will be distributed in a GIVEAWAY accessible only to MATH holders.
To enter this giveaway, send 0.000001 MATH to raffle.mathmakesart.tez (tz1VjyQmYo1a7CfUKmMJqtYi6MxisWgcSfou).
Giveaway rewards will not be sent out until after the BURN date.

NOTE: Each wallet address is allowed at most 1 entry in the giveaway.
Sending more than 0.000001 MATH will NOT increase your chances of winning.
Sending MATH to other addresses to increase your chance of winning will lead to disqualification from both this giveaway event and future MATH airdrops.
